            >
              Digitalkan <span class="gradient-text">Ekosistem</span>
              <br />
              <span id="hero-title" class="text-white">Pendidikan Anda</span>
            </h1>
            <p
              id="hero-desc"
              class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 mb-12 leading-relaxed font-medium reveal-on-scroll max-w-xl mx-auto lg:mx-0"
            >
              Platform manajemen keuangan sekolah terpadu dengan standar
              keamanan enterprise untuk transparansi finansial institusi Anda.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div
            class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 justify-center lg:justify-start reveal-on-scroll"
          >
            <a href="/layanan" class="btn-primary min-w-[200px]">
              Pelajari Fitur
            </a>
            <a
              href="#kontak"
              class="px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-black text-lg glass border border-white/10 text-white hover:bg-white/10 transition-all"
            >
              Konsultasi
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 3D Card / App Mockup (Iconix Style) -->
        <div class="flex-1 w-full lg:max-w-none reveal-on-scroll relative">
          <!-- Decorative 3D Elements -->
          <div
            class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-32 h-32 bg-syntax-emerald/20 blur-3xl rounded-full animate-bounce duration-[5000ms]"
          >
